select count(*) as aggregate from (select `ads_properties`.`id` as `ads_property_id`, CONCAT('http://127.0.0.1:8000/storage/', media.id, '/', media.file_name) AS image_path, `ads`.`title`, `ads`.`slug`, `users`.`name` as `name_user`, `ads_properties`.*, `ads`.`status`, `media`.`id` as `media_id`, `media`.`file_name` as `file_name`, `ads`.`is_active`,
(6371 * acos(
cos(radians(-6.1571072))
* cos(radians(ads_properties.lat))
* cos(radians(ads_properties.lng) - radians(106.774528))
+ sin(radians(-6.1571072))
* sin(radians(ads_properties.lat))
)) AS distance
from `ads_properties` inner join `ads` on `ads`.`id` = `ads_properties`.`ads_id` inner join `media` on `media`.`model_id` = `ads`.`id` and media.id = (SELECT MIN(id) FROM media WHERE media.model_id = ads.id) inner join `users` on `users`.`id` = `ads`.`user_id` where `ads`.`type` = 'property' and (`ads`.`title` like '%%' or `users`.`name` like '%%' or `ads_properties`.`ads_type` like '%%' or `ads`.`status` like '%%' or `ads`.`is_active` like '%%') having `distance` < 300) as `aggregate_table`
